        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Greater Supervision In Banking Act of 2021 or the GSIB Act of 2021 </b></p> <p>This bill requires certain large bank holding companies (also known as global systemically important banks) to annually report on, among other things, their size and complexity, enforcement and regulatory actions taken against them, capital market activity, employee compensation, employee diversity, and environmental impacts. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
